originalText.text: I actively expressed that I no longer use weight to help me understand my health. I had to state this three times in order to decline a weight check. Additionally, while I did not bring up size, nutrition, or movement - Dr. Li explicitly told me that I needed to lose weight and “get rid of my tummy.” After seeing my breast reduction scars and the size of my chest, she laughed while asking “well what was the point?” Do NOT go here if you are in a larger body and looking for a safe, size-inclusive appointment.

originalText.text: The absolute worst doctor I have ever been too. She ignored all of the health issues that I told her about. Instead she decided to lecture me on how I should be more active and find a less stressful job ! I have no  idea where she went to medical school but I am convinced that she is not even a real doctor ! She wasted my time and money ! I complained of serious health problems chest pains, and possible kidney infection which she gave me no help with ! She just wrote it off as no big deal. She spent time asking me personal questions instead. But still thought that her terrible service was worth 300 ! Insane ! Do yourself a favor and find another doctor ! She is garbage !
